jacdac.AirPressureReg.MaxPressure:
Constant hPa u22.10 (uint32_t). Highest air pressure that can be reported.

const [maxPressure] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u22.10")
```
jacdac.AirPressureReg.MinPressure:
Constant hPa u22.10 (uint32_t). Lowest air pressure that can be reported.
* ```
const [minPressure] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u22.10")
```
jacdac.AirPressureReg.Pressure:
Read-only hPa u22.10 (uint32_t). The air pressure.

```
jacdac.AirPressureReg.PressureError:
Read-only hPa u22.10 (uint32_t). The real pressure is between `pressure - pressure_error` and `pressure + pressure_error`.
* ```
const [pressureError] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u22.10")
```
modules.AirPressureClient: A sensor measuring air pressure of outside environment.
modules.AirPressureClient.maxPressure: Highest air pressure that can be reported.
modules.AirPressureClient.minPressure: Lowest air pressure that can be reported.
modules.AirPressureClient.onPressureChan: Run code when the pressure changes by the given threshold value.
modules.AirPressureClient.pressureError: The real pressure is between `pressure - pressure_error` and `pressure + pressure_error`.
